page.title: 17T.V. IN OGWELL AND DENBURY
page.content: We have four channels on T.V.BBC 1 BBC 2 TSW and channel 4.BBC stands for british broadcasting centre but it has not changed my life that much. my favourte tv programs are 1.THE V 2.YOUNG ONES 3.BMX PRO CYCLES 4.Q.E.D The V is about these aleins that have landed on earth.and they eat anything they can find. Young ones is comedy. BMX pro cycling is racing round a track Q.E.D is documentry about peoples lives. We have 6 sides on our tv and 4 work and the others do not work. Andrew Devonsh1ire. Jason Fosdike. Aged 10
